A Mexican businessman died in a
crash in the same helicopter incoming president Enrique Pena
Nieto used during his campaign, Reforma newspaper reported
today.  Juan Armando Hinojosa Garcia and two pilots died in the
accident over the weekend in Mexico state, hours after the
businessman met with Pena Nieto, the Mexico City-based newspaper
